{
  "stem": "10353.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I heard that you can also get some protection papers from the Swiss embassy, that the Swiss embassy is issuing citizenship papers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I made my way to the Swiss embassy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And although it was-- it was guarded by the Arrow Cross and also by the gendarmes, because the way Budapest is built, it can easily be cut off from either side of the street, because it's more or less built in squares.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I made my way through and I slipped into the Swiss embassy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I got into the Swiss embassy, there was a Dr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Somogyi there who knew me from before, and I knew him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I begged him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I says, please take me in, because by that time, there was already an accumulation of people in the Swiss embassy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He says, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Go upstairs and try to find yourself a little place, a corner where you can-- you can be.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was there overnight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But the following day, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Dr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Somogyi came and he gave me one of those Swiss citizenship papers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He says, here is this paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't know how much help it will be, but I'm sorry to tell you that you have to go.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You are not allowed to stay here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But what happened, if you ran out from the Swiss embassy, the Arrow Cross and the gendarmes were standing there and they rounded you up right away.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They took you away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But I had to get out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was ordered to get out, so I got out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And lo and behold, they did round us up and they formed a column of certain-- I don't remember how many, about 60, 80 people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they put us in rows of 5.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
